Least squares formula

\[ Y \sim X\mathbf{a} + b \] \[ \sum_{i=1}^n(y_i-\hat{y_i})^2=\sum_{i=1}^n(y_i-(\mathbf{x_i}^T\mathbf{a}+b))^2 =||Y-(X\mathbf{a}+b)||^2 \] \(\mathbf{a}b\)

\(b=0\) \[ ||Y-X\mathbf{a}||^2=(Y-X\mathbf{a})^T(Y-X\mathbf{a})=(Y^T-\mathbf{a}^TX^T)(Y-X\mathbf{a}) \] \(\mathbf{a}^TX^TYY^TX\mathbf{a}\) \[ Y^TY-2Y^TX\mathbf{a}+\mathbf{a}^TX^TX\mathbf{a} \] 0\(\mathbf{a}\) \[ -2Y^TX+(X^TX\mathbf{a})^T+\mathbf{a}^TX^TX=-2Y^TX+2\mathbf{a}^TX^TX=0 \] \[ \mathbf{a}^T=Y^TX(X^TX)^{-1} \] \[ \mathbf{a}=(X^TX)^{-1}X^TY \]

b=0b0 X1 \[ X'=\left(\begin{array}{ccc} \mathbf{x_1}&1\\ \mathbf{x_2}&1\\ .&.\\ .&.\\ .&.\\ \mathbf{x_n}&1 \end{array} \right) \]

\(\mathbf{a}\)1b

\[ \mathbf{a'}= \left( \begin{array}{ccc} a_1\\a_2\\.\\.\\.\\a_n\\b \end{array} \right ) \]

\[ y_i=X'\mathbf{a'}[i,]=\mathbf{x_i}^T\mathbf{a}+b \] b=0

d<-3
n<-1000
X<-matrix(rnorm(d*n),ncol=d)
a<-rnorm(d)
b<-rnorm(1)
y<-X%*%a+b+rnorm(n)*0.1
plot(X[,1],y)
abline(b,a,col=2)

plot(X[,2],y)
abline(b,a,col=2)

plot(X[,3],y)
abline(b,a,col=2)
